 <script type="text/javascript">
    var cache = {};
    $(function () {
      $( "#search" ).autocomplete({
        minLength: 2,
        maxResults: 20,
        source: function( request, response ) {
          var term = request.term;
          if ( term in cache ) {
            response( cache[ term ] );
            return;
          }
 
          $.getJSON( "/autocomplete", request, function( data, status, xhr ) {
            cache[ term ] = data;
            response( data );
          });
        },
        select: function( event, ui ) {
          event.preventDefault();
          $( "label[for='local'] strong" ).html(decodeURIComponent(ui.item.value.replace(/\+/g, ' ')));
          $("#search").val('Aguarde...').addClass('loading');
          location.href = '/' + ui.item.custom;
          /*return false;*/
        }
      }).autocomplete( "instance" )._renderItem = function( ul, item ) {
        return $( "<li>" )
          .append( "<div>" + decodeURIComponent(item.label.replace(/\+/g, ' ')) + "</div>" )
          .appendTo( ul );
      };
    });
</script>

         <script type="text/javascript">

      	var mapInit = null;

        var stylesWarnings = {
          'Polygon': new ol.style.Style({
            stroke: new ol.style.Stroke({
              color: '#777',
              width: 1
            }),
            fill: new ol.style.Fill({
              color: 'rgba(255, 192, 0, 0.65)'
            })
          }),
          'FFC000': new ol.style.Style({
            stroke: new ol.style.Stroke({
              color: '#777',
              width: 1
            }),
            fill: new ol.style.Fill({
              color: 'rgba(255, 192, 0, 0.65)'
            })
          }),
          'FAFF03': new ol.style.Style({
            stroke: new ol.style.Stroke({
              color: '#777',
              width: 1
            }),
            fill: new ol.style.Fill({
              color: 'rgba(250, 255, 3, 0.65)'
            })
          }),
          'F20602': new ol.style.Style({
            stroke: new ol.style.Stroke({
              color: '#777',
              width: 1
            }),
            fill: new ol.style.Fill({
              color: 'rgba(242, 6, 2, 0.65)'
            })
          }),
          '000000': new ol.style.Style({
            stroke: new ol.style.Stroke({
              color: '#777',
              width: 1
            }),
            fill: new ol.style.Fill({
              color: 'rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65)'
            })
          }),
          'C3C3C3': new ol.style.Style({
            stroke: new ol.style.Stroke({
              color: '#777',
              width: 1
            }),
            fill: new ol.style.Fill({
              color: 'rgba(195, 195, 195, 0.65)'
            })
          })
        };

        var styleFunctionWarnings = function(feature) {
          if(feature.get('cor'))
              return stylesWarnings[feature.get('cor')];
          else
              return stylesWarnings[feature.getGeometry().getType()];
        };

        var periodoSelecionado = 24;

        var vectorSourceWarnings = new ol.source.Vector({
          url: 'https://www.cptec.inpe.br/avisos/' + periodoSelecionado + '.geojson',
          projection: 'EPSG:4326',
          format: new ol.format.GeoJSON()
        });

        var vectorLayerWarnings = new ol.layer.Vector({
          source: vectorSourceWarnings,
          style: styleFunctionWarnings
        });

        var mapWarnings = new ol.Map({
          controls: ol.control.defaults({
            attributionOptions: {
              collapsible: false
            }
          }),
          view: new ol.View({
            center: [-54.101389, -14.598889],
            projection: 'EPSG:4326',
            zoom: 4
          })
        });

      var element = document.getElementById('popup');

      var popup = new ol.Overlay({
          element: element,
          positioning: 'bottom-center',
          stopEvent: false,
          offset: [0, -50]
      });

      mapWarnings.addOverlay(popup);

      mapWarnings.on('click', function(evt) {
          var feature = mapWarnings.forEachFeatureAtPixel(evt.pixel,
              function(feature) {
                  return feature;
              }
          );
          
          if (feature && feature.getGeometry().getType() == 'Polygon') {
              if ($('.popover').is(':visible')) {
                  $(element).popover('dispose');
              }
              var geometry = feature.getGeometry()
              var extent = geometry.getExtent();
              popup.setPosition(getCenterOfExtent(extent));

              $(element).popover({
                  'placement': 'bottom',
                  'html': true,
                  'content': '<b>' + feature.get('tipo_aviso') + ' - ' + feature.getId() + '</b><br><br>* ' + feature.get('fenomenos').join('<br>* ') + '<br><br><a href="//tempo.cptec.inpe.br/avisos/area/' + feature.getId() + '" target="_blank">Mais detalhes >></a>' 
              });
              $(element).popover('show');
          } else {
              $(element).popover('dispose');
          }
      });

      mapWarnings.on('pointermove', function(e) {
          if (e.dragging) {
              $(element).popover('dispose');
              return;
          }
          var pixel = mapWarnings.getEventPixel(e.originalEvent);
          var hit = mapWarnings.hasFeatureAtPixel(pixel);
      });

      $("input[type='radio'][name='options']").change(function() {
          if($(this).val() != periodoSelecionado) {
            periodoSelecionado = $(this).val();
            if ($('.popover').is(':visible')) {
              $(element).popover('dispose');
            }
            var periodo = $(this).data('periodo');
            vectorLayerWarnings.setSource(new ol.source.Vector({
              url: 'https://www.cptec.inpe.br/avisos/' + periodoSelecionado + '.geojson',
              projection: 'EPSG:4326',
              format: new ol.format.GeoJSON()
            }));
          }
      });

    $('.opcoes-menu a[data-toggle="tab"]').on('shown.bs.tab', function (e) {
    	var tInd = (e.target).toString().lastIndexOf('#');

    	console.log("Elemento: " + (e.target).toString().substring(tInd).trim() + "------- " + periodoSelecionado + " - " + mapInit);

    	if((e.target).toString().substring(tInd).trim() == '#avisos') {
        	if(mapInit === null) {
        		console.log((e.target).toString().lastIndexOf('#'));
        		mapWarnings.setTarget(document.getElementById('mapa-avisos'));
        		mapWarnings.addLayer(new ol.layer.Tile({source: new ol.source.OSM({"url" : "http://mt0.google.com/vt/lyrs=m&hl=en&x={x}&y={y}&z={z}"})}));
        		mapWarnings.addLayer(vectorLayerWarnings);
        		mapInit = true;
        	}
        }
    });

      function getCenterOfExtent(Extent){
          var X = Extent[0] + (Extent[2]-Extent[0])/2;
          var Y = Extent[1] + (Extent[3]-Extent[1])/2;
          return [X, Y];
      }

      </script>
